Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:02:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji and Usopp snuck aboard\Nthe Ark Maxim to rescue Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they've been aware\Nof us for a long while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know?! What're we gonna do?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split up inside and\Nhead straight for the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Luffy had a gold ball\Nattached to his arm by Eneru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was thrown from the Maxim\Ninto the ruins of Shandora,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he got back up to settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright... Dammit!\NI can't get this gold ball off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp saved Nami in the nick of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unable to stand up to Eneru's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they found themselves\Ntrapped in a corner, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-kun!\N--Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to ask... for a light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Capriccio for Despair-- Looming\NDestruction of the Sky Islands!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pay... you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You'll pay for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Ninside the ship just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gears have gone awry... I must fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Nami fell safely\Ninto some Island Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:05:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the jungle, not the ruins...\NFocus on falling into the Island Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp Hopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I jumped too far! I jumped too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm falling! I'm gonna crash!\NI'm gonna crash and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! I forgot to unhook it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice! Nami! Sounds like\Nyou're all right! That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Sanji-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry you had to get all\Ncharred like this just for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe! N-Nami!\NPull me outta here, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why won't you come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Blue Sea man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is not so easily brought down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fully acquainted with\Nthis ship's drive circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without electric power,\Nthe wind power from the 200 Jet Dials
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered from my homeland of Birka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will keep the ship afloat for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you feeble beings try...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this land will meet its end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! That huge vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the same one I saw in the ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these are the Island Clouds up above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruins? Oh, the city of gold?! It exists?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But all the gold is in Eneru's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Zoro and the others\Nshould be in the ruins below!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"\N"Current Location"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:12.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:12.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"\N"Current Location"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:13.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruins of Shandora"\N"Current Location"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the topography or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I do know it's dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find everyone and get off this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no safe places left here in Skypiea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Not that way! Left! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I can't turn so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't destroy my hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Jack's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit destroying stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spewing out thunderclouds nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rat scurried off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so restless and shrewd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter. The festivities are soon at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin and the others are gone!\NZoro and Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Wyper and God...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they've already gone up it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way things stand, this land,\NSkypiea, will be annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky island will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Our village, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he'd return\Neveryone in the sky to the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the sky islands... going to disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper and the others are right through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is headed for the grand belfry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the\Nnavigator and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're on board, could that mean they're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down there! Luffy! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You grew hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:57.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gyaaaaa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that gold on your arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! The gold bell is at\Nthe top of this vine, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Eneru's after it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the belfry does exist, it'd have to be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gyaaaaa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But he's already...\N--All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where our\Nnavigator is? She has orange hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? If you mean Nami, she's on that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I only hear one\Nvoice coming from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigator! Long-nose! Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa! Thank goodness! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! A guerilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Everyone's been taken out!\NOh, if only I'd been there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Aisa! Where's Luffy?!\NWasn't he with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy just went up the vine\Nto rescue you from Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Crap! We just missed each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left just now. I tried to stop him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about bad timing! There's no\Ntime left! We gotta escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! I'll go after him on the waver!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just get to the Merry somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That ship's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on, quickly! The sky is\Ngetting darker and darker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You need to escape at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief... Aisa still hasn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. She hasn't returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa is a bright child. Let us have\Nfaith she is with some warriors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't make it through this\Nwithout the ships in the dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd have to go around the long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Use dials to create rivers\Ninside the island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Please go to Cloud End\Nand escape to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru plans to eliminate this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, you'll all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last six years,\Nwhat we've known most of all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that Eneru has the\Npower to bring us despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that the time is imminent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of waiting\Nfor a miracle to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you pray... Before you\Nturn a blind eye to reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to do what you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time where you could survive\Nif you lie low as a victim is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take action!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect your own life\Nby blaming someone later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now! Make the\Ndecision to leave this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many islanders are left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still half of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more baggage allowed!\NGet all the islanders out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Leave the\Ntwo-billion-Extol-per-person departure fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazon-san! You need to escape, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--Hurry! To Cloud End!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--This land...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?\N--It's about to be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then. Let us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...begin the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaragan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dawdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lightning is getting bigger and bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boats in the port have been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the western end of the beach!\NQuickly! There are still boats there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly! Toss your belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! You need to get on a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Warrior Calgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What huge lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna end up sky dust if we stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Hurry to the ship!\NI'll get Luffy and bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-All right! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta carry these guys\Nto the ship somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We have no time! Can you walk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru! So you've started it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry. There's nothing we can do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Luffy can deal with\Nan enemy flying into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it in time! We gotta escape\Nbefore this land is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An exquisite view!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume things are gonna\Nturn out how you want, Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some 400 years ago,\Nthere was a man known as a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one believed him as he was\Nexecuted for his great lies and trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth was still passed on\Nin the clouds high above!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Led by a Bell's Sound! Tale of\Nthe Great Warrior and the Explorer"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
